snippet.title: Little Dragons Café - Explore a massive world
snippet.description:
On today's menu - Exploration

Discover an amazing world brought to life by legendary developer Yasuhiro Wada - the creator of the original Harvest Moon®. Encounter exotic wildlife, gather ingredients you’ll need, uncover secret areas, and make sure you bring a friend along for help. 
Remember, there’s always more to see at... Little Dragons Café.
